---
title: John Dory & Asian-Style Salad with Sesame Dressing & Coriander
description: Delicate white fish, bursting with juicy flavour, sit atop a vibrant Asian-style salad drizzled in a zesty sesame dressing. Fresh coriander adds a fragrant finish, making every bite a perfect harmony of crunch, tang, and spice. Need we say more? Dig in!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*

